021143425/http://www.wort.lu/en/view/state-council-objects-to-new-adoption-law-51af2a2ce4b0e794460f86dd |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lequotidien.lu/politique-et-societe/45647.html|title=Luxembourg: Le Conseil d'État balaie le compromis|date=6 June 2013|publisher=Le Quotidien|language=fr|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113070753/http://www.lequotidien.lu/politique-et-societe/45647.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年6月19日，法律事務委員會決定給予同性伴侶全面領養的權利。該法案本來會在當年秋天被表決<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wort.lu/en/view/breakthrough-in-adoption-law-reform-for-same-sex-couples-51c186b1e4b0c60d7f091524|title=Breakthrough in adoption law reform for same-sex couples|publisher=Wort.lu|date=19 June 2013|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2013-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021143427/http://www.wort.lu/en/view/breakthrough-in-adoption-law-reform-for-same-sex-couples-51c186b1e4b0c60d7f091524|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lessentiel.lu/fr/news/luxembourg/story/L-adoption-pleniere-pour-les-couples-homosexuels--17740265|title=L'adoption plénière pour les couples homosexuels?|publisher=L'essentiel|date=19 June 2013|language=fr|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625161251/http://www.lessentiel.lu/fr/news/luxembourg/story/L-adoption-pleniere-pour-les-couples-homosexuels--17740265|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，但是2013年10月因為盧森堡政府辭職而引發的選舉延遲了對此的投票<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lessentiel.lu/fr/news/luxembourg/story/20025665|title=Adoption et mariage gay devront attendre|date=25 July 2013|publisher=L'essentiel|language=fr|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625161206/http://www.lessentiel.lu/fr/news/luxembourg/story/20025665|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

